{"tid":2423784,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"何超儀獨力投資荷里活電影邀奧斯卡導演合作 在香港搭美國景拍","createTime":"2021-02-26T06:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T06:51:22.000Z","uid":318316,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1b33bb5cb58cfeb6f92c35b17fd9746a1db08fb6","tid":2423784,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"今日，由曾獲提名奧斯卡最佳導演的Mike Figgis執導，何超儀主演的荷里活電影《Mother Tongue》於邵氏影城舉行開鏡儀式，並安排舞獅助興，超儀主持點睛儀式，她跟擔任電影監製的陳子聰齊向導演拜年獲贈利是。 <br />\n<br />\n由於疫情關係，原本於美國拍攝轉為香港，導演Mike Figgis表示好的故仔無論在哪裏拍攝也可以，疫情來說覺得香港比較安全，還有一眾好演員。超儀指導演好實驗式，不介意來港玩，她說：「<strong>因疫情影響，原本在加州開鏡也做不到，我們沙膽地向導演表示在香港也有辦法拍到加州風味，所以都幾揼本，在邵氏最大的廠搭建一間巨屋。」 </strong><br />\n<br />\n超儀指該片屬懸疑、驚慄和令人反思的藝術片，內容關於扭曲的家庭，這次更是超儀從影以來首次一人分飾兩角。 她稱該片改編自著名小說家及編劇家Bruce Wagner 的小說《The Marvel Universe》，並由Bruce Wagner親自撰寫劇本。 <br />\n<br />\n其他演員包括剛與Johnny Depp合演新片的Minami、Julian Sands、Tomoko Nawata及金燕玲等，導演讚超儀選角有眼光，之前都是靠網上視像與演員試鏡。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/v2/article/02Ew6D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fv2%2Farticle%2F02Ew6D&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd68yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=cfd72197\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/v2/article/02Ew6D</a><br />\n<br />\n日本演員Minami 。<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hW7SmqFqeCBhuFB5Tjqh3T1RCC3ddeBsbCiJZBzF6Vi9CJx0aByYULk1BVSsQc09GACdCf0sTEykWI0dOVycU/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hW7SmqFqeCBhuFB5Tjqh3T1RCC3ddeBsbCiJZBzF6Vi9CJx0aByYULk1BVSsQc09GACdCf0sTEykWI0dOVycU%2Fw1200&h=fe9b32d1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本演員 Tomoko Nawata<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXAiiaF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXAiiaF.jpg&h=31d73657&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbvNVXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbvNVXg.jpg&h=f7822cc2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mC9yRvF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmC9yRvF.jpg&h=b39bf16c&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ki8vTJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKi8vTJU.jpg&h=306e2231&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVax63U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVax63U.jpg&h=8e3f8f2a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h58Qv8qS9ahdsD3xcjLIVQFZZaXhfY3kUCDk7CDNhNCBAPH8VBT11IU8IZyVIPC1JAjwneUAPcSYUOCVBVTx1/w1200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0h58Qv8qS9ahdsD3xcjLIVQFZZaXhfY3kUCDk7CDNhNCBAPH8VBT11IU8IZyVIPC1JAjwneUAPcSYUOCVBVTx1%2Fw1200&h=c06690a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f735e73ae9b61fac789058c09760b805a79c7ddd","tid":2423784,"uid":7147,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"對波大小小可以拍av"},{"pid":"99b0bd8069bd7223a6df446d7b413a73ac78fb68","tid":2423784,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f735e73ae9b61fac789058c09760b805a79c7ddd","tid":2423784,"uid":7147,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"對波大小小可以拍av"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:28:06.000Z","msg":"咁既資質係av界會紅唔起"},{"pid":"cdfb6f3cf5832b895b9227df8f228d93fdfe2a60","tid":2423784,"uid":61284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:30:07.000Z","msg":"第二個有冇ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e3c681d70d15a2c71739cb9140703e461810b6","tid":2423784,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdfb6f3cf5832b895b9227df8f228d93fdfe2a60","tid":2423784,"uid":61284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:30:07.000Z","msg":"第二個有冇ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Eu6KdK3UU